{"tid":598189,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"軋斷腳掌：涉事司機任地產代理　涉危駕被捕","createTime":"2018-03-19T10:03:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-20T23:51:18.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"4e444e59fa7a3a0a28a511e96dcae03d6afc0ab9","tid":598189,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T10:03:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180319/photo/bkn-20180319170450129-0319_00822_001_01b.jpg?20180319175611\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180319%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180319170450129-0319_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20180319175611&h=d5ccaa72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n寶馬失控剷上小巴站。(張世洋攝)<br />\n<br />\n涉案姓陳（28歲）寶馬司機涉嫌危險駕駛引致他人身體嚴重受傷被捕，其後已獲准保釋候查，須於4月中旬向警方報到。據了解，陳任職地產代理，其Fb除上載有家庭照外，亦有樓市資訊、與同事工作、聚會時相片，以及招聘廣告，招攬有志人士加入地產界。去年中，他上載一張維港海景相片，表示希望日後能帶同事一起出海慶祝，相信他當時正參加遊艇聚會。過往他曾多次轉載分享企業管理的語錄名言，以激勵自己，其中一張相片，寫有「一個人承擔責任的能量，是未來承載財富的能量」。<br />\n<br />\n東網記者致電聯絡其上司時，對方指陳今日有上班，惟中途外出處理事務，現時正了解其最新情況。另外，記者到訪陳位於梨木樹邨的單位時，一名中年女親友應門，表示對陳涉及車禍一事「乜都唔知」，隨即關門。根據運輸署資料顯示，肇事寶馬房車於2015年首次登記，姓陳車主當時以逾40萬港元購入。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180319/photo/bkn-20180319170450129-0319_00822_001_02b.jpg?20180319175611\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180319%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180319170450129-0319_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20180319175611&h=8dd2035a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳在Fb上載維港景色，盼日後帶同事出海慶祝。(互聯網)<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180319/bkn-20180319170450129-0319_00822_001.html?refer=hn2&amp;eventsection=hk_news&amp;eventid=402882b06203b88301623d0e71a22a23\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180319%2Fbkn-20180319170450129-0319_00822_001.html%3Frefer%3Dhn2%26eventsection%3Dhk_news%26eventid%3D402882b06203b88301623d0e71a22a23&d=dYNBpw77B42fMm44Tyl9p%2B9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=7f7daee2\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180319/bkn-20180319170450129-0319_00822_001.html?refer=hn2&amp;eventsection=hk_news&amp;eventid=402882b06203b88301623d0e71a22a23</a>"},{"pid":"0f3364a9e26df78694569aafe04f5ec770940874","tid":598189,"uid":62060,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T10:09:58.000Z","msg":"地產狗！"},{"pid":"768755e06c3df580e91e35e66096b0a2b58fb74e","tid":598189,"uid":88029,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T10:12:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"99db062d3c217ab4d743825ebb0170a90de56b60","tid":598189,"uid":127123,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"768755e06c3df580e91e35e66096b0a2b58fb74e","tid":598189,"uid":88029,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T10:12:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T10:14:03.000Z","msg":"公屋車場多名車是常識吧"},{"pid":"d200c1583bda3227c23f7cd4bd78a993ab2f5661","tid":598189,"uid":71257,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T10:17:30.000Z","msg":"中二病地產狗 祝佢坐監個陣老豆老母生癌中風死"},{"pid":"40dc894fbed4aafe49a9958c6663db897c5e94cf","tid":598189,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"768755e06c3df580e91e35e66096b0a2b58fb74e","tid":598189,"uid":88029,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T10:12:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T10:21:39.000Z","msg":"住公屋既地產狗充大頭是常識吧"},{"pid":"6cea72108bfa0a78e8c854ec6026d896391632f0","tid":598189,"uid":106204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T10:22:27.000Z","msg":"地產狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56a7a37b0589315529d24b78f90d9e69f20b1e68","tid":598189,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T10:24:17.000Z","msg":"住公屋用40萬買車<br />\n我真係屌你老母"},{"pid":"2494dfdbd26cf0d30caf02106d31828abcbe6881","tid":598189,"uid":61280,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T10:24:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquo